Metadata: Northwest Fish Hatchery Newsletter (Volume 4, Number 1 and Number 2, March and November 1988)
Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program
Two newsletter issues in one entry for 1988.

Some topics of interest in these newsletter issues include: Guillotine for Tagged Fish, D. Ewing; Hold the Formalin? By B. Nyara. Oxolinic Acid Knocks Out Cold Water Disease, G. Nandor; Iodophores Don't Kill Bugs in Unfertilized Eggs, J. Banks; Spawning by Computer, D. Ewing.
